---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service - Quistra" description="Read Quistra's Terms of Service.">
  <Header />

  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: August 10, 2025</p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of Quistra (the "Services"). By using the Services, you agree to these Terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Use of the Services</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>You must be at least 13 years old to use the Services.</li>
        <li>You are responsible for the content you post and for complying with applicable laws.</li>
        <li>Do not abuse, interfere with, or disrupt the Services.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Content</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        You retain ownership of the content you submit. By posting, you grant us a worldwide, non-exclusive license to host, store, and display your content to operate the Services.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        The Services are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee accuracy, availability, or reliability.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, Quistra and its affiliates shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Termination</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We may suspend or terminate access to the Services at any time for any reason, including violations of these Terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Changes to the Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of the Services after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Questions about these Terms? Reach out via our <a href="/contact" class="text-coral-600 hover:text-coral-500">Contact</a> page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
